<title>
Air Cleaner Filter Inspection
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove air cleaner filter. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1406002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that filter is not excessively dirty, damaged or oily. Clean filter with compressed air from air outlet side of filter.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAW101020005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.526mm" ver = "01" gw = "157" gh = "113"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install air cleaner filter. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1406002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
